Posts.Content: hi liz i have a painful spot come up in my breast every now and again in the same spot..i have had 2 mammograms done and nothing showed up..thankfully. .mine were from consuming too much caffiene..i also took vitamin E caps daily for a few weeks.i watch my caffiene intake and it has been quite a while since i have had it...you should be seen by your doc before you take my advice though..just to be safe..
Posts.Title: Found lump, but now its gone
